-- Jacobs group cuts Adecco holding
-- 
-- Wed Mar 12, 2014 01:11PM EDT
-- None



LONDON, March 12 (Reuters) - The Jacobs group is to sell a 16 percent stake in Adecco <ADEN.VX>, the world's largest staffing agency, the investment group said on Thursday, in an accelerated bookbuilding which will reduce its stake to 2.5 percent as it attempts to diversify its portfolio.

